headline: Valley Bank Appoints Curt Lang to Chief Banking Officer for New Jersey
summary: MORRISTOWN, N.J., November 17, 2025--Valley National Bancorp announces the appointment of Curt Lang as the Chief Banking Officer for New Jersey.
